LEX Escrow


"Buyer" is	 a person

"Payee" is A person

"Agent" is  a person

"Service Fee" is	aN  amount


The Buyer pays an amount into escrow, appoints the Payee, appoints the Agent, and fixes the Service Fee


CLAUSE: Pay Out

The Agent may pay from escrow the Service Fee to themselves, and afterwards pay the remainder of the escrow to the Payee


CLAUSE: Pay Back

The Agent may pay from escrow the Service Fee to themselves, and afterwards return the remainder of the escrow to the Buyer


